tp://www.1905.com/news/20151124/951443.shtml#p1|archive-date=2015-11-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年8月7日正式杀青，进入后期制作阶段。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1905.com/news/20150808/920304.shtml|language=|title=张艺谋《长城》杀青 影片将进入后期制作阶段|publisher=1905电影网|date=2015-08-08|accessdate=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150810172040/http://www.1905.com/news/20150808/920304.shtml|archive-date=2015-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>

